title: Court stops Botswana deporting Eritrean soccer players
text: GABORONE, Botswana (AP) â€” A group of 10 players from Eritrea's national football team that are claiming asylum in Botswana after a World Cup qualifier have won a temporary reprieve, with a court ruling they shouldn't be sent back home.
